title: CANAL / WORKER barks
description: Barks for workers loitering by the canal after fixing the water lock.

dialogueTree.english: "Fixin' the world one water lock at a time."

dialogueTree.english: "Good job, boys. Now who wants to flick it?"

dialogueTree.belarusian: „Добрая праца, хлопцы. Хто хоча крутануць рычаг?”

dialogueTree.title: Canal Crew: ""Hey, let the police flick the swit..."
dialogueTree.english: "Hey, let the police flick the switch!"

dialogueTree.title: Canal Crew: ""So... where's the next broken wate..."
dialogueTree.english: "So... where's the next broken water lock?"

dialogueTree.title: Canal Crew: ""Let's run out the clock. Lunch is..."
dialogueTree.english: "Let's run out the clock. Lunch is at 14 anyway."
dialogueTree.polish: „Poobijajmy się trochę. O 14:00 i tak jest przerwa obiadowa”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: „Паб'емся крыху. А 14:00 усё роўна абедзенны перапынак.”
